title: How come I havent got my 10 years anniversary icon yet?
body: I have yet to receive my icon and i was playing during the weekend and week it was announced.

replies.body: You haven't received the gifts yet because we're not done sending it out per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  There are a lot of accounts so it's going to take some time.  Patience!
